import React from 'react' export default function Section2() { return (

DISCOVER PARASOL

What is Parasol Finance?

Parasol Finance is the first community governed IDO platform built on Solana.

Governance

With the unique Parasol system, the community decides which projects are put forward and can participate.

Built on Solana

With Solana you enjoy low fees and fast transaction and flexibility. Explore our token on explorer here .

Parasol Token (PSOL)

Parasol token owners will be able to participate in projects, you will have to hold your tokens for about 6 months.

) }
